{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Introducing \u201cDark Grim Mariupolis\u201d, a point'n'click adventure game set in a world, combining noir, Greek mythology, magic, mysticism, hopeless entourage of Greco-Roman Age of Decadence and stifling everyday routine. Encourage yourself and step into darkness\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enter Mariupolis, a dark place accompanied with confusing, strange music of no visible source. You are some sort of a detective, and therefore you need to investigate, but why? That\u2019s the thing you\u2019re going to find out\u2026 or, maybe not. Everything depends on you and sudden whims of Pentaculus, a grim god stretching its hands out over the whole city. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Investigate and solve puzzles, while resisting dark and obscure grasp of Mariupolis, where the only things guarding you from its baneful influence are sarcasm and arrogance. And be aware \u2013 your hero might actually die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Steal another\u2019s property to find out the truth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve puzzles and conduct investigations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reply in appropriate manner in dialogs to achieve your goals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sometimes you\u2019ll have to make a moral choice.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deceive and hide your true intensions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complain about life, work and social order.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Bad Trip","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/597730/76539ecd465bbfc010a32c7d25556f7d738c6080.jpg"},{"name":"Ooo... Orange?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/597730/cbf89055f0d1f5adda008aa6ebeb8de8a945a675.jpg"},{"name":"Thor's Hammer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/597730/792b476b2